OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773162677
OL,3,CFive members of Iranian women's
OL,4,Cfootball team granted asylum in
OL,5,CAustralia
OL,7,FFive members of the Iranian women's
OL,8,Ffootball team have been granted asylum
OL,9,Fby Australia where they had been
OL,10,Fplaying in the AFC Women's Asian Cup.
OL,12,FUS President Donald Trump joined
OL,13,FIranian groups urging the Australian
OL,14,Fgovernment to help the women after
OL,15,Fthey were knocked out of the
OL,16,Ftournament over the weekend and faced
OL,17,Fthe prospect of returning to a country
OL,18,Funder bombardment and possible
OL,19,Fpunishment by the regime for not
OL,20,Fsinging the national anthem before
OL,21,Ftheir opening match.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773162677
OL,3,CFive members of Iranian women's
OL,4,Cfootball team granted asylum in
OL,5,CAustralia
OL,7,FEarly on Tuesday, Australian federal
OL,8,Fpolice officers transported five of
OL,9,Fthe women from their hotel in Gold
OL,10,FCoast, Australia, "to a safe location"
OL,11,Fafter they made asylum requests.
OL,12,FThere, they met with Home Affairs
OL,13,FMinister Tony Burke where their
OL,14,Fhumanitarian visas was finalised, the
OL,15,Fminister told reporters in Brisbane
OL,16,Fhours later.
OL,26,@rD@SOUrD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
