CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773162677
OL,3,CFive members of Iranian women's
OL,4,Cfootball team granted asylum in
OL,5,CAustralia
OL,7,F"I don't want to begin to imagine how
OL,8,Fdifficult that decision is for each of
OL,9,Fthe individual women, but certainly
OL,10,Flast night it was joy, it was relief,"
OL,11,Fsaid Burke, who posted photos to
OL,12,Fsocial media of the women smiling and
OL,13,Fclapping as he signed documents.
OL,14,F"People were very excited about
OL,15,Fembarking on a life in Australia."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@fO]vD@AOUwD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773162677
OL,3,CFive members of Iranian women's
OL,4,Cfootball team granted asylum in
OL,5,CAustralia
OL,7,FConcerns were raised for the safety of
OL,8,Fmembers of the team following their
OL,9,Fdefeat in the tournament after they
OL,10,Fwere labelled traitors by members of
OL,11,Fthe Iranian regime for staying silent
OL,12,Fduring the national anthem at the
OL,13,Fbeginning of their first match last
OL,14,Fweek.
OL,16,FThe women granted asylum were happy
OL,17,Ffor their names and pictures to be
OL,18,Fpublished, he said. Burke added that
OL,19,Fthe players wanted to make clear that
OL,20,Fthey were "not political activists."
OL,26,@|D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
