FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773162677
OL,3,CFive members of Iranian women's
OL,4,Cfootball team granted asylum in
OL,5,CAustralia
OL,7,FReza Pahlavi, the son of Iran's ousted
OL,8,Fshah, had also joined calls for the
OL,9,Fwomen's safety to be ensured by the
OL,10,FAustralian government. He named the
OL,11,Ffootballers who he said had fled the
OL,12,Fteam for safety as Fatemeh Pasandideh,
OL,13,FZahra Ghanbari, Zahra Sarbali, Atefeh
OL,14,FRamazanzadeh and Mona Hamoudi.
OL,16,FThe Iranian team arrived in Australia
OL,17,Ffor the Women's Asian Cup last month,
OL,18,Fbefore the Iran war began on February
OL,19,F28.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
