OL,3,CFive members of Iranian women's
OL,4,Cfootball team granted asylum in
OL,5,CAustralia
OL,7,FIran's head coach Marziyeh Jafari said
OL,8,Fon Sunday the players "want to come
OL,9,Fback to Iran as soon as we can".
OL,11,FAn official squad list named 26
OL,12,Fplayers, plus Jafari and other
OL,13,Fcoaches. Burke said the offer of
OL,14,Fasylum was extended to all on the team.
OL,16,FIt was not clear when the remaining
OL,17,Fplayers were due to leave Australia,
OL,18,Fbut on Tuesday members of the public
OL,19,Fkneeled or lay in front of a white bus
OL,20,Fwith tinted windows believed to be
OL,21,Fcarrying the rest of the team.
OL,26,@pD@WOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
