OL,3,CFive members of Iranian women's
OL,4,Cfootball team granted asylum in
OL,5,CAustralia
OL,7,FThe protesters, some wearing red,
OL,8,Fwhite and green clothing or holding
OL,9,Fpre-Revolution Iranian flags, tried to
OL,10,Fprevent the bus from departing the
OL,11,Fhotel. Some chanted "Save our girls"
OL,12,Fand "Please act now."
