OL,3,CFive members of Iranian women's
OL,4,Cfootball team granted asylum in
OL,5,CAustralia
OL,7,FDuring the tournament, the women have
OL,8,Fmostly declined to comment on the
OL,9,Fsituation at home, although Iran
OL,10,Fforward Sara Didar choked back tears
OL,11,Fin a news conference Wednesday as she
OL,12,Fshared their concerns for their
OL,13,Ffamilies and all Iranians.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
