OL,3,CFive members of Iranian women's
OL,4,Cfootball team granted asylum in
OL,5,CAustralia
OL,7,FThe Iranian team has drawn national
OL,8,Fnews coverage in Australia after the
OL,9,Fplayers' silence during the anthem
OL,10,Fbefore an opening loss to South Korea
OL,11,Flast week was viewed by some as an act
OL,12,Fof resistance and others as a show of
OL,13,Fmourning. The team hasn't clarified.
OL,14,FThey later sang and saluted during the
OL,15,Fanthem before their remaining two
OL,16,Fmatches.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
