PN,31110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773162677
OL,3,CFive members of Iranian women's
OL,4,Cfootball team granted asylum in
OL,5,CAustralia
OL,7,F"Australians have been moved by the
OL,8,Fplight of these brave women," Prime
OL,9,FMinister Anthony Albanese told
OL,10,Freporters Tuesday. "They're safe here
OL,11,Fand they should feel at home here."
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@]O]rD@TOUsD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
