CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773162677
OL,3,CFive members of Iranian women's
OL,4,Cfootball team granted asylum in
OL,5,CAustralia
OL,7,FAustralia's announcement came after
OL,8,FTrump called on Australia to grant
OL,9,Fasylum to any team member who wanted
OL,10,Fit. Earlier that day, Trump had
OL,11,Flambasted Australia on social media,
OL,12,Fsaying Australia was "making a
OL,13,Fterrible humanitarian mistake by
OL,14,Fallowing the ... team to be forced
OL,15,Fback to Iran, where they will most
OL,16,Flikely be killed." Trump added: "The
OL,17,FU.S. will take them if you won't."
OL,26,@xD@RO]xD@aOUyD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
