OL,3,CFive members of Iranian women's
OL,4,Cfootball team granted asylum in
OL,5,CAustralia
OL,7,FLess than two hours later, in another
OL,8,Fsocial media post, Trump praised
OL,9,FAlbanese, saying, "He's on it! Five
OL,10,Fhave already been taken care of, and
OL,11,Fthe rest are on their way."
OL,13,FAlbanese said Trump had called him for
OL,14,F"a very positive conversation," about
OL,15,Fthe matter. The Australian leader had
OL,16,Fexplained "the action that we'd
OL,17,Fundertaken over the previous 48
OL,18,Fhours," to support the women.
OL,26,@qD@SOUsD@[O]vD@AOUvD@_O]xD@KOUzD@GO]
